1
00:01:25,370 --> 00:01:27,170
- WHAT DO YOU WANT?

2
00:01:27,203 --> 00:01:31,670
- I AM SOMEONE WHO,
LIKE YOURSELF,
DESPISES INUYASHA.

3
00:01:31,703 --> 00:01:35,537
- I SHOULD KNOW THE NAME
OF THE ONE I MAKE A PACT WITH.

4
00:01:35,570 --> 00:01:37,737
- MY APOLOGIES.

5
00:01:37,770 --> 00:01:40,103
CALL ME NARAKU.

6
00:01:40,137 --> 00:01:41,337
- WELL, I'M NOT AFRAID.

7
00:01:41,370 --> 00:01:42,970
NARAKU'S A TERRIBLE DEMON.

8
00:01:43,003 --> 00:01:45,270
WE'VE GOT TO DO WHAT WE CAN
TO DESTROY HIM.

9
00:01:45,303 --> 00:01:51,303
- TRYING TO BUY TIME IN ORDER TO
SAVE THE LIVES OF YOUR FRIENDS.

10
00:01:51,837 --> 00:01:57,003
[GRUNTING]
- AAH!

11
00:02:03,370 --> 00:02:05,970
- WHAT'S GOING ON?

12
00:02:06,003 --> 00:02:08,770
- I WAS AFRAID.

13
00:02:08,803 --> 00:02:10,270
- HMM?
AH--

14
00:02:10,303 --> 00:02:13,103
AAH!

15
00:02:19,237 --> 00:02:20,803
- UHH!

16
00:02:20,837 --> 00:02:23,637
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING
THAT FOR, INUYASHA?
UHH.

17
00:02:23,670 --> 00:02:25,270
- LAY OFF!
- IF YOU SEAL UP THE WELL,

18
00:02:25,303 --> 00:02:27,403
KAGOME WILL NEVER BE ABLE
TO RETURN TO THIS ERA.

19
00:02:27,437 --> 00:02:30,970
DON'T FOOL YOURSELF.
YOU NEED HER AS MUCH AS
THE REST OF US DO.

20
00:02:31,003 --> 00:02:32,137
- I CAN'T HAVE HER
HANGING AROUND.

21
00:02:32,170 --> 00:02:35,770
OTHERWISE, I'LL NEVER BE ABLE
TO FIGHT THE WAY I WANT TO.

22
00:02:35,803 --> 00:02:37,737
[GRUNTING]

23
00:02:37,770 --> 00:02:41,737
WHOA.
[GROWLS]

24
00:02:41,770 --> 00:02:43,237
LET'S GO, MIROKU.

25
00:02:43,270 --> 00:02:45,470
- GO?
TO WHERE?

26
00:02:45,503 --> 00:02:46,837
- HOW CAN YOU ASK SUCH A THING?

27
00:02:46,870 --> 00:02:50,437
WE'LL FIND NARAKU AND CRUSH HIM
ONCE AND FOR ALL.

28
00:02:50,470 --> 00:02:52,337
- LET'S BE GOING, SHIPPO.

29
00:02:52,370 --> 00:02:53,070
- NOT ME.

30
00:02:53,103 --> 00:02:55,970
I DESPISE INUYASHA.
[SNIFFLING]

31
00:02:56,003 --> 00:02:57,237
- FINE WITH ME.
STAY HERE.

32
00:02:57,270 --> 00:03:00,170
- I UNDERSTAND THAT YOU FORCED
KAGOME TO LEAVE FOR HER SAFETY,

33
00:03:00,203 --> 00:03:03,137
BUT DO YOU NOT THINK YOU
COULD HAVE ACHIEVED THE SAME END

34
00:03:03,170 --> 00:03:04,703
THROUGH LESS AGGRESSIVE METHODS?

35
00:03:04,737 --> 00:03:06,337
- LEAVE ME ALONE!
I DID WHAT I HAD TO!

36
00:03:06,370 --> 00:03:09,370
- SO HOW DO YOU RECOMMEND WE
GO ABOUT SEARCHING FOR NARAKU?

37
00:03:09,403 --> 00:03:12,037
YOU'VE COME ACROSS SOME
NEW LEADS, I SUPPOSE?

38
00:03:12,070 --> 00:03:14,103
- NO, NOT EXACTLY.

39
00:03:14,137 --> 00:03:15,870
- YOU HAVE NOTHING TO GO ON.
- QUIET!

40
00:03:15,903 --> 00:03:17,370
- YOU SENT KAGOME BACK
OF YOUR OWN VOLITION.

41
00:03:17,403 --> 00:03:20,737
I'D APPRECIATE IT IF YOU DIDN'T
TAKE OUT YOUR FRUSTRATION ON ME.

42
00:03:20,770 --> 00:03:21,870
- WILL YOU GET OFF MY BACK?!

43
00:03:21,903 --> 00:03:25,137
- OUR BEST HOPE NOW
LIES IN COMPOSING OURSELVES

44
00:03:25,170 --> 00:03:26,703
AND THINKING THINGS THROUGH.

45
00:03:26,737 --> 00:03:28,103
- I DON'T HAVE TIME FOR THIS!

46
00:03:28,137 --> 00:03:29,203
- WHAT ARE YOU THINKING?

47
00:03:29,237 --> 00:03:33,170
I WANT TO CRUSH NARAKU
AS DESPERATELY AS YOU, INUYASHA.

48
00:03:33,203 --> 00:03:35,637
50 YEARS AGO,
HE FORMED A WIND TUNNEL

49
00:03:35,670 --> 00:03:36,803
ON THE HAND OF MY GRANDFATHER,

50
00:03:36,837 --> 00:03:41,137
AND NOW THE CURSE HAS CARRIED
OVER THE GENERATIONS TO ME.

51
00:03:41,170 --> 00:03:43,737
- MIROKU...

52
00:03:45,103 --> 00:03:48,570
TAKING ACTION IS MORE MY STYLE,
NOT STRATEGIZING.

53
00:03:48,603 --> 00:03:49,637
YOU THINK OF SOMETHING.

54
00:03:49,670 --> 00:03:50,837
- WORK WITH ME, INUYASHA.

55
00:03:50,870 --> 00:03:52,270
LET'S GO BACK TO WHEN
THIS ALL STARTED.

56
00:03:52,303 --> 00:03:55,503
YOU MENTIONED THAT YOU FELL INTO
NARAKU'S TRAP 50 YEARS AGO

57
00:03:55,537 --> 00:03:57,770
IN THIS VERY SAME VILLAGE,
CORRECT?

58
00:03:57,803 --> 00:03:58,770
- YEAH.

59
00:03:58,803 --> 00:04:01,903
- SO THEN YOU'VE MET NARAKU
IN PERSON, HAVE YOU?

60
00:04:01,937 --> 00:04:03,703
- NOT EXACTLY.

61
00:04:04,537 --> 00:04:07,370
- INUYASHA, YOU CAN BECOME
FULLY HUMAN

62
00:04:07,403 --> 00:04:08,737
IF YOU USE THE SACRED JEWEL.

63
00:04:08,770 --> 00:04:12,337
I SHALL BRING IT TO YOU TOMORROW
AT THE BREAK OF DAWN

64
00:04:12,370 --> 00:04:15,237
TO THIS VERY PLACE.

65
00:04:16,370 --> 00:04:18,503
- HUH?
UH?

66
00:04:18,537 --> 00:04:21,337
- DIE, INUYASHA!

67
00:04:21,370 --> 00:04:23,703
[GRUMBLES]

68
00:04:23,737 --> 00:04:27,303
- I MAY HAVE MET HIM,
BUT IF I DID,
HE WAS DISGUISED AS KIKYO,

69
00:04:27,337 --> 00:04:29,503
SO I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT HE LOOKS LIKE.

70
00:04:29,537 --> 00:04:30,803
- IT MAKES NO SENSE.

71
00:04:30,837 --> 00:04:31,737
YOU DON'T KNOW NARAKU,

72
00:04:31,770 --> 00:04:33,237
AND YET HE DESPISED YOU ENOUGH

73
00:04:33,270 --> 00:04:34,870
TO DISGUISE HIMSELF AS KIKYO

74
00:04:34,903 --> 00:04:36,003
AND LEFT YOU FOR DEAD.

75
00:04:36,037 --> 00:04:37,537
COULD YOU HAVE DONE SOMETHING
IN THE PAST

76
00:04:37,570 --> 00:04:38,670
TO CAUSE HIM TO BE EMBITTERED?

77
00:04:38,703 --> 00:04:42,203
- HOW DO I KNOW?
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHAT HE LOOKS LIKE.

78
00:04:42,237 --> 00:04:43,237
- HMM.

79
00:04:43,270 --> 00:04:46,303
ONE THING WE DO KNOW IS THAT
KIKYO WAS A PRIESTESS.

80
00:04:46,337 --> 00:04:47,503
[SOBBING]

81
00:04:47,537 --> 00:04:49,270
PERHAPS IT WAS SHE AND NOT YOU

82
00:04:49,303 --> 00:04:50,770
THAT NARAKU HAD
A DEEP GRUDGE AGAINST,

83
00:04:50,803 --> 00:04:52,970
ESPECIALLY SINCE YOU DON'T THINK
YOU KNOW HIM.

84
00:04:53,003 --> 00:04:56,303
- YOU MEAN, IT'S KIKYO HE HATES?

85
00:05:00,770 --> 00:05:02,937
- KAGOME!
- HUH?

86
00:05:02,970 --> 00:05:05,003
- HI.
LONG TIME, NO SEE.

87
00:05:05,037 --> 00:05:06,203
SO HOW'S YOUR RHEUMATISM?

88
00:05:06,237 --> 00:05:08,037
- YEAH, AND YOUR
PLANTAR'S WARTS?

89
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:09,003
[LAUGHS NERVOUSLY]

90
00:05:09,037 --> 00:05:12,137
- YOU'RE WEARING CIVVIES.
UNIFORM IN THE WASH?

91
00:05:12,170 --> 00:05:12,970
- MM-HMM.

92
00:05:13,003 --> 00:05:14,903
I'M STILL TRYING
TO GET THE STAINS OUT.

93
00:05:14,937 --> 00:05:17,570
THE FRONT WAS COVERED IN BLOOD.
[GASPS]

94
00:05:17,603 --> 00:05:20,270
- NOW YOU'RE A HEMOPHILIAC?

95
00:05:20,303 --> 00:05:21,103
- OH, YEAH.

96
00:05:21,137 --> 00:05:24,637
I'LL BE 6 FEET UNDER
IN NO TIME AT ALL.

97
00:05:28,437 --> 00:05:32,103
INUYASHA'S BLEEDING
HADN'T STOPPED.

98
00:05:32,137 --> 00:05:35,003
I WAS SO WORRIED ABOUT HIM.

99
00:05:36,703 --> 00:05:39,037
BUT MAYBE HE HAD
OTHER THINGS ON HIS MIND

100
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:41,603
WHEN HE HELD ME IN HIS ARMS.

101
00:05:41,637 --> 00:05:43,003
- I'LL HANG ON TO THE JEWEL.

102
00:05:43,037 --> 00:05:46,637
- MAYBE HE HUGGED ME
TO GET THE SACRED SHIKON JEWEL.

103
00:05:46,670 --> 00:05:49,737
THAT CREEP'S GONNA PAY!
- KAGOME.

104
00:05:49,770 --> 00:05:53,803
TAKE IT INTO THE HALL
IF YOU DON'T MIND.

105
00:05:54,037 --> 00:05:56,570
- IT WAS THE FIRST TIME
A GUY HUGGED ME LIKE THAT.

106
00:05:56,603 --> 00:06:00,137
I COULDN'T HELP IT
IF I GOT A BIT FLUSTERED.

107
00:06:00,337 --> 00:06:01,803
HE'S A GUY, AFTER ALL, RIGHT?

108
00:06:01,837 --> 00:06:06,203
I MEAN, HE'S HALF-DEMON,
BUT HE'S ALSO HALF-HUMAN.

109
00:06:15,203 --> 00:06:16,503
[SIPS]

110
00:06:16,537 --> 00:06:17,503
- THESE INJURIES ARE SERIOUS.

111
00:06:17,537 --> 00:06:19,637
YE WON'T BE SEEING ANY BATTLES
FOR SOME TIME YET.

112
00:06:19,670 --> 00:06:22,103
- THEY WON'T HOLD ME BACK
ANY LONGER THAN 2 OR 3 DAYS.

113
00:06:22,137 --> 00:06:25,137
- NOT SURPRISING THAT YE WOULD
PUT ON A BRAVE FACE.

114
00:06:25,170 --> 00:06:26,903
THERE.
- AAH!

115
00:06:26,937 --> 00:06:28,170
WHAT'D YOU DO THAT FOR?!

116
00:06:28,203 --> 00:06:29,570
- IF YE CAN MUSTER
THAT MUCH VIGOR,

117
00:06:29,603 --> 00:06:32,070
THEN PERHAPS IT WON'T
TAKE TOO LONG TO RECOVER.

118
00:06:32,103 --> 00:06:34,003
I NEED TO SPEAK TO YE.

119
00:06:34,037 --> 00:06:35,870
I HAVE GIVEN MUCH THOUGHT
TO THIS,

120
00:06:35,903 --> 00:06:37,237
EVER SINCE MY SISTER KIKYO

121
00:06:37,270 --> 00:06:40,803
WAS REVIVED BY
THE EVIL WITCH URASUE.

122
00:06:40,837 --> 00:06:41,670
- HMM.

123
00:06:41,703 --> 00:06:44,203
- KIKYO HAD TOLD ME
IT WAS YE, INUYASHA,

124
00:06:44,237 --> 00:06:47,870
WHO HAD STOLEN HER
SACRED SHIKON JEWEL.

125
00:06:47,903 --> 00:06:50,670
DO YE NOT THINK IT STRANGE?

126
00:06:50,703 --> 00:06:52,903
THE ONE WHO
DISGUISED HIMSELF AS YE

127
00:06:52,937 --> 00:06:55,237
COULD HAVE MADE OFF
WITH THE JEWEL,

128
00:06:55,270 --> 00:06:57,537
YET HE DID NOT.

129
00:06:57,570 --> 00:07:00,470
HE TRICKED YE INTO
TERRORIZING THE VILLAGE

130
00:07:00,503 --> 00:07:03,537
AND PURSUING THE SACRED JEWEL.

131
00:07:03,737 --> 00:07:05,737
THEN KIKYO BOUND YE TO A TREE

132
00:07:05,770 --> 00:07:07,137
WITH HER SACRED ARROW.

133
00:07:07,170 --> 00:07:10,337
WAS THE TRICKSTER ATTEMPTING
TO PIT YE AGAINST EACH OTHER?

134
00:07:10,370 --> 00:07:13,037
OR WAS IT KIKYO WHO WAS
THE TRUE OBJECT OF HIS MALICE?

135
00:07:13,070 --> 00:07:17,103
WAS HE TRYING TO FILL HER HEART
WITH HATRED AND BITTERNESS?

136
00:07:17,137 --> 00:07:18,170
- WHAT?

137
00:07:18,203 --> 00:07:19,170
- IN KIKYO'S POSSESSION,

138
00:07:19,203 --> 00:07:22,470
THE SACRED JEWEL OF THE 4 SOULS
REMAINED PURE,

139
00:07:22,503 --> 00:07:25,370
BUT WHEN HER HEART
BECAME TAINTED AND HATEFUL,

140
00:07:25,403 --> 00:07:27,037
THE JEWEL ALSO BECAME SULLIED,

141
00:07:27,070 --> 00:07:30,303
AND IT FILLED
WITH A MALEVOLENT POWER.

142
00:07:30,337 --> 00:07:33,103
AT THE TIME, THERE WAS
BUT A SINGLE PERSON

143
00:07:33,137 --> 00:07:36,437
WHO WISHED FOR
SUCH A TERRIBLE OUTCOME.

144
00:07:37,037 --> 00:07:39,270
SHALL I TAKE YE TO SEE THE PLACE

145
00:07:39,303 --> 00:07:42,103
WHERE THIS MAN ONCE RESIDED?

146
00:07:44,937 --> 00:07:47,803
KIKYO HAD COME
TO HER OWN DECISION.

147
00:07:47,837 --> 00:07:49,503
- SHE WAS HARBORING A THIEF.

148
00:07:49,537 --> 00:07:50,637
- BECAUSE SHE PITIED HIM.

149
00:07:50,670 --> 00:07:54,303
HE WAS UNABLE
TO MOVE ON HIS OWN.

150
00:07:58,070 --> 00:07:59,237
THIS IS THE CAVE.

151
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:03,070
THE MAN WENT BY
THE NAME OF ONIGUMO.

152
00:08:06,370 --> 00:08:08,037
HE SUFFERED FROM TERRIBLE BURNS,

153
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:10,137
AND HIS FACE WAS
ESPECIALLY SCARRED.

154
00:08:10,170 --> 00:08:12,203
I KNOW NOT IF
HE FELL FROM A CLIFF

155
00:08:12,237 --> 00:08:14,203
OR HOW HE SUSTAINED
HIS INJURIES,

156
00:08:14,237 --> 00:08:15,603
BUT BOTH LEGS WERE BROKEN.

157
00:08:15,637 --> 00:08:20,303
YET DESPITE HIS SEVERE WOUNDS,
ONIGUMO CONTINUED TO ENDURE.

158
00:08:20,337 --> 00:08:21,603
HE DID NOT MOVE AGAIN,

159
00:08:21,637 --> 00:08:24,637
BUT HE RECOVERED HIS STRENGTH
ENOUGH TO CONVERSE,

160
00:08:24,670 --> 00:08:28,970
AND, GRADUALLY,
HIS TRUE NATURE EMERGED.

161
00:08:32,137 --> 00:08:33,337
- YOU...

162
00:08:33,370 --> 00:08:35,470
YOUNG LASS.

163
00:08:35,503 --> 00:08:37,203
- IT'S KAEDE.

164
00:08:37,237 --> 00:08:38,603
- YES.

165
00:08:38,637 --> 00:08:42,837
YOUR SISTER POSSESSES WHAT IS
KNOWN AS THE SHIKON JEWEL,
DOES SHE NOT?

166
00:08:42,870 --> 00:08:45,037
- WHAT WOULD YE KNOW
ABOUT THE JEWEL?

167
00:08:45,070 --> 00:08:49,470
- ALL WHO ARE WICKED
KNOW OF IT AND PURSUE IT.

168
00:08:49,503 --> 00:08:50,537
- YE INCLUDED?

169
00:08:50,570 --> 00:08:53,703
- I UNDERSTAND THAT
THE MORE EVIL THE JEWEL ABSORBS,

170
00:08:53,737 --> 00:08:57,170
THE MORE EVIL IT BECOMES.
OUTSTANDING.

171
00:08:57,203 --> 00:08:59,437
- MY SISTER HAS IT
UNDER HER CONTROL.

172
00:08:59,470 --> 00:09:01,070
IT WON'T BE CORRUPTED.

173
00:09:01,103 --> 00:09:03,503
- KIKYO'S MANNER
IS SELF-RIGHTEOUS.

174
00:09:03,537 --> 00:09:05,570
FOR ONCE, I SHOULD
LIKE TO SEE HER

175
00:09:05,603 --> 00:09:07,437
APPREHENSIVE AND FRIGHTENED.

176
00:09:07,470 --> 00:09:10,203
THAT WOULD BRING ME
TRUE PLEASURE.

177
00:09:10,237 --> 00:09:12,570
[CHUCKLING]

178
00:09:12,603 --> 00:09:16,437
- I SEE.
ONIGUMO SAID THAT, DID HE?

179
00:09:16,470 --> 00:09:19,237
- BIG SISTER, I DON'T CARE FOR
THAT MAN.

180
00:09:19,270 --> 00:09:21,403
- BEAR HIM NO GRUDGE.

181
00:09:21,437 --> 00:09:22,337
GIVE HIM PITY.

182
00:09:22,370 --> 00:09:24,003
HIS INJURIES ARE GREAT.

183
00:09:24,037 --> 00:09:26,603
HE SHALL NEVER MOVE
FROM THERE AGAIN.

184
00:09:26,637 --> 00:09:28,237
- IT WAS NOT LONG AFTERWARD

185
00:09:28,270 --> 00:09:32,737
THAT KIKYO BOUND YE TO A TREE
WITH HER ARROW.

186
00:09:33,570 --> 00:09:37,403
SEVERAL DAYS LATER, WHEN I WENT
TO VISIT ONIGUMO AT THE CAVE,

187
00:09:37,437 --> 00:09:39,337
I FOUND IT HAD BEEN BURNED OUT.

188
00:09:39,370 --> 00:09:40,370
JUDGING BY WHAT I SAW,

189
00:09:40,403 --> 00:09:42,437
THE FLAMES MUST HAVE
BEEN INTENSE,

190
00:09:42,470 --> 00:09:44,370
FOR ONIGUMO WAS UNABLE TO MOVE

191
00:09:44,403 --> 00:09:46,403
AND WOULD HAVE PERISHED
IN THE CAVE,

192
00:09:46,437 --> 00:09:48,870
YET HIS BONES WERE
NOWHERE TO BE FOUND.

193
00:09:48,903 --> 00:09:51,537
THEY, TOO, MUST HAVE
GONE UP IN FLAMES.

194
00:09:51,570 --> 00:09:53,070
- WHAT DOES THIS
HAVE TO DO WITH ME?

195
00:09:53,103 --> 00:09:55,937
I'M LOOKING FOR NARAKU,
AND NARAKU IS A DEMON,

196
00:09:55,970 --> 00:09:59,037
NOT A HUMAN,
SUCH AS THIS ONIGUMO PERSON.

197
00:09:59,070 --> 00:10:00,370
- NO MISTAKING THAT.

198
00:10:00,403 --> 00:10:04,037
ONIGUMO MAY HAVE BEEN EVIL,
BUT HE WAS HUMAN--

199
00:10:04,070 --> 00:10:05,537
A SCOURGE TO HUMANITY.

200
00:10:05,570 --> 00:10:09,670
- LET'S GO INSIDE
AND TAKE A LOOK, SHALL WE?

201
00:10:11,603 --> 00:10:13,570
[GRUNTING]

202
00:10:13,603 --> 00:10:15,170
- OH!
WHOA!

203
00:10:15,203 --> 00:10:17,637
OH, I CAN'T PULL IT
OUT OF THE WELL,

204
00:10:17,670 --> 00:10:20,737
AND UNLESS I DO,
KAGOME WILL NEVER RETURN TO US.

205
00:10:20,770 --> 00:10:24,470
I'M STARTING
TO MISS HER ALREADY.

206
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:28,003
- I CAN'T HAVE HER
HANGING AROUND.

207
00:10:28,037 --> 00:10:31,203
OTHERWISE, I'LL NEVER BE ABLE
TO FIGHT THE WAY I WANT TO.

208
00:10:31,237 --> 00:10:34,303
- UNH!
HE'S MORE STUBBORN THAN A MULE!

209
00:10:34,337 --> 00:10:35,103
THAT DOES IT!

210
00:10:35,137 --> 00:10:37,770
I'M NEVER SPEAKING
TO INUYASHA AGAIN!

211
00:10:37,803 --> 00:10:41,370
- DID YOU SAY THE NAME INUYASHA?

212
00:10:41,403 --> 00:10:43,970
[WHIMPERING]

213
00:10:44,503 --> 00:10:47,370
I ASKED YOU A QUESTION.

214
00:10:47,403 --> 00:10:48,770
- WHOA!

215
00:10:48,803 --> 00:10:52,537
- HUH.
LADY KAEDE.
- HMM?

216
00:10:52,570 --> 00:10:53,437
- LOOK THERE.

217
00:10:53,470 --> 00:10:54,270
THIS ONE SIDE ALONE

218
00:10:54,303 --> 00:10:57,737
IS FREE OF GRASS AND MOSS
OF ANY KIND.

219
00:10:57,770 --> 00:10:58,737
- OH.

220
00:10:58,770 --> 00:10:59,870
IT'S THE SAME PLACE.

221
00:10:59,903 --> 00:11:03,403
THIS IS THE VERY SITE
WHERE ONIGUMO LAY INJURED.

222
00:11:03,437 --> 00:11:05,370
- HMM.
HUH?

223
00:11:05,403 --> 00:11:06,237
AH!
UNH!

224
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:08,103
I'M SENSING THE EVIL SPIRIT
OF A DEMON,

225
00:11:08,137 --> 00:11:11,037
AN ENTITY WHICH HAS BEEN
LEFT BEHIND HERE FOR DECADES.

226
00:11:11,070 --> 00:11:12,170
- IMPOSSIBLE.

227
00:11:12,203 --> 00:11:14,703
- COULD IT BE A HUMAN THAT
LEFT THIS FOUL SPIRIT BEHIND,

228
00:11:14,737 --> 00:11:17,137
HERE WHERE EVEN
GRASS REFUSES TO GROW?

229
00:11:17,170 --> 00:11:20,170
- THE SPIRIT IN THIS CAVE
BELONGS TO NO HUMAN.

230
00:11:20,203 --> 00:11:22,203
IT'S DEFINITELY THAT OF A DEMON.

231
00:11:22,237 --> 00:11:24,437
- HMM.
BUT IF ONIGUMO WAS HUMAN,

232
00:11:24,470 --> 00:11:26,903
HOW COULD HE HAVE POSSESSED
THE SPIRIT OF A DEMON?

233
00:11:26,937 --> 00:11:29,370
- HELP!
- HUH?
- SOMEBODY HELP ME!

234
00:11:29,403 --> 00:11:32,037
AAH! AAH!
- [DOGS BARKING]

235
00:11:32,070 --> 00:11:33,803
- SHIPPO!
UHH!

236
00:11:33,837 --> 00:11:35,037
[GRUNTING]
AAH!

237
00:11:35,070 --> 00:11:39,403
- [SNARLING]
- IRON REAPER SOUL STEALER!

238
00:11:41,403 --> 00:11:42,837
UHH!

239
00:11:43,403 --> 00:11:44,770
UHH.

240
00:11:44,803 --> 00:11:46,970
- ARE YOU STILL IN PAIN?

241
00:11:47,003 --> 00:11:49,737
OH--YOUR CHEST!
YOU'RE BLEEDING!

242
00:11:49,770 --> 00:11:53,103
- NO.
MY WOUND MUST HAVE REOPENED.

243
00:11:53,137 --> 00:11:53,770
HUH?

244
00:11:53,803 --> 00:11:56,170
- MIGHT YOU BE INUYASHA?

245
00:11:56,203 --> 00:11:57,937
- THAT DEPENDS WHO'S ASKING!

246
00:11:57,970 --> 00:12:01,937
- I AM ROYAKAN,
THE GUARDIAN OF HAOWA.

247
00:12:01,970 --> 00:12:03,037
- ROYAKAN.

248
00:12:03,070 --> 00:12:06,470
ARE YE NOT THE GENTLE CREATURE
THAT GUARDS THE FOREST?

249
00:12:06,503 --> 00:12:08,937
- THAT WAS BEFORE I WAS REBORN.

250
00:12:08,970 --> 00:12:13,637
INUYASHA, I HAVE COME
TO SLAY YOU!

251
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:15,003
ARRGGH!

252
00:12:15,037 --> 00:12:16,703
- GOOD LUCK, IS ALL I CAN SAY.

253
00:12:16,737 --> 00:12:22,070
- ROYAKAN SEEMS TO KNOW
THAT INUYASHA'S
IN NO CONDITION TO FIGHT.

254
00:12:22,103 --> 00:12:25,103
[GRUNTING]

255
00:12:28,870 --> 00:12:31,970
FIGHT AS YOU MAY,
YOU CAN NEVER DEFEAT ME!

256
00:12:32,003 --> 00:12:33,970
ARRGGH!

257
00:12:34,003 --> 00:12:36,737
- THAT LEAVES ME
WITH ONE CHOICE.

258
00:12:42,770 --> 00:12:43,803
- AAH!

259
00:12:43,837 --> 00:12:47,470
- INUYASHA!
QUICKLY, THIS WAY!

260
00:12:47,503 --> 00:12:51,037
ARRGGH!

261
00:12:52,203 --> 00:12:53,870
[GRUMBLES]

262
00:12:55,270 --> 00:12:56,570
[CHUCKLING]

263
00:12:56,603 --> 00:12:58,670
- I MUST CONGRATULATE MYSELF.

264
00:12:58,703 --> 00:13:00,437
IT WAS A BRILLIANT IDEA, INDEED,

265
00:13:00,470 --> 00:13:03,803
EMBEDDING A JEWEL SHARD
IN ROYAKAN'S BODY.

266
00:13:03,837 --> 00:13:07,337
- IRON REAPER!

267
00:13:07,370 --> 00:13:09,237
UNH...
- YOU OK?

268
00:13:09,270 --> 00:13:13,337
- MY VISION IS STARTING
TO BECOME BLURRY.

269
00:13:14,970 --> 00:13:16,737
- MONK, INUYASHA IS IN DANGER.

270
00:13:16,770 --> 00:13:18,637
- I'M MOVING AS FAST
AS I'M ABLE.

271
00:13:18,670 --> 00:13:21,070
BUT FIRST--UNH!--

272
00:13:21,103 --> 00:13:23,003
I MUST STOP ROYAKAN.

273
00:13:23,037 --> 00:13:24,337
[GROWLING]

274
00:13:24,370 --> 00:13:26,903
[GRUNTING]
IT CAN BE DONE!

275
00:13:26,937 --> 00:13:29,470
[GROWLING]

276
00:13:45,403 --> 00:13:48,070
HE ESCAPED.
HUH?

277
00:13:48,103 --> 00:13:49,103
- HOW UNFORTUNATE.

278
00:13:49,137 --> 00:13:53,370
PERHAPS I SHOULD HAVE MADE
ROYAKAN MORE POWERFUL.

279
00:13:53,403 --> 00:13:55,737
- INUYASHA, SHOW ME YOUR WOUNDS.

280
00:13:55,770 --> 00:13:57,737
- WHERE IS ROYAKAN?

281
00:13:57,770 --> 00:13:58,703
- HE HAS FLED.

282
00:13:58,737 --> 00:14:01,103
- INUYASHA, I SENSE THAT
NARAKU IS NEAR.

283
00:14:01,137 --> 00:14:03,903
- WHAT?
- MOST LIKELY,
ROYAKAN HAS A JEWEL FRAGMENT

284
00:14:03,937 --> 00:14:06,037
AND, THROUGH IT, IS BEING
MANIPULATED BY NARAKU.

285
00:14:06,070 --> 00:14:09,937
- THAT WOULD EXPLAIN
SUCH A GENTLE CREATURE
TURNING EVIL.

286
00:14:09,970 --> 00:14:12,437
[GRUNTING]
INUYASHA!

287
00:14:12,470 --> 00:14:14,703
- NARAKU, WHERE ARE YOU?

288
00:14:14,737 --> 00:14:19,470
COME OUT AND FACE ME,
ONE-ON-ONE!
[GRUNTING]

289
00:14:19,503 --> 00:14:21,370
- INUYASHA!

290
00:14:21,403 --> 00:14:23,837
- ROYAKAN MAY RETURN
FOR ANOTHER ATTACK.

291
00:14:23,870 --> 00:14:25,603
WE SHOULD FLEE
TO THE VILLAGE AT ONCE

292
00:14:25,637 --> 00:14:28,870
AND CONTEMPLATE OUR NEXT MOVE.

293
00:14:28,903 --> 00:14:31,470
- INUYASHA.

294
00:14:50,884 --> 00:14:52,284
[SIGH]

295
00:14:52,317 --> 00:14:54,017
- IT'S BEEN 3 WHOLE DAYS.

296
00:14:54,051 --> 00:14:56,017
WHY DOESN'T HE COME AND GET ME?

297
00:14:56,051 --> 00:14:56,984
- KAGOME!
- HUH?

298
00:14:57,017 --> 00:14:58,884
- GUESS WHAT--
HOJO HAS BEEN LOOKING

299
00:14:58,917 --> 00:15:00,117
ALL OVER THE PLACE FOR YOU.

300
00:15:00,151 --> 00:15:03,917
- HOW HAVE YOU BEEN
FEELING THESE DAYS, KAGOME?
ANY BETTER?

301
00:15:03,951 --> 00:15:05,917
- YEAH, I GUESS.
- HEY, GREAT.

302
00:15:05,951 --> 00:15:09,717
THEN HOW ABOUT SEEING A MOVIE
WITH ME THIS SATURDAY?

303
00:15:09,751 --> 00:15:10,784
- THIS SATURDAY?

304
00:15:10,817 --> 00:15:13,584
- YEAH.
I'LL BRING A THERAPEUTIC
BACK PAD FOR YOU.

305
00:15:13,617 --> 00:15:16,384
OR HAVE YOU MADE
OTHER PLANS ALREADY?

306
00:15:16,417 --> 00:15:18,251
- WELL, NOT EXACTLY.

307
00:15:18,284 --> 00:15:21,784
INUYASHA WILL COME FOR ME
BY THEN, WON'T HE?

308
00:15:21,817 --> 00:15:22,951
- JUST SAY YES.

309
00:15:22,984 --> 00:15:26,417
- YOU TOTALLY BLEW HIM OFF
LAST TIME YOU HAD A DATE, RIGHT?

310
00:15:26,451 --> 00:15:28,251
- HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT?

311
00:15:28,284 --> 00:15:30,751
- EXCUSE US.
WON'T BE LONG.

312
00:15:30,784 --> 00:15:31,684
- AAH!

313
00:15:31,717 --> 00:15:33,317
UNH!
WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?

314
00:15:33,351 --> 00:15:35,284
- YOU'VE GOT THE HOTS
FOR SOME OTHER GUY,

315
00:15:35,317 --> 00:15:36,584
DON'T YOU, KAGOME?
- UH...

316
00:15:36,617 --> 00:15:38,617
- THAT EXPLAINS ALL THE SIGNS
COMING FROM YOU LATELY.

317
00:15:38,651 --> 00:15:42,151
- I DIDN'T THINK YOU WERE
MEMORIZING CHEMISTRY EQUATIONS.

318
00:15:42,184 --> 00:15:43,684
- HANG ON A MINUTE.

319
00:15:43,717 --> 00:15:46,384
HOW WAS I SUPPOSED TO ACT?

320
00:15:46,417 --> 00:15:47,217
- AHA!

321
00:15:47,251 --> 00:15:50,584
YOU LOVE HIM,
BUT HE DOESN'T LOVE YOU.

322
00:15:50,617 --> 00:15:51,651
- OH, GIVE ME A BREAK!

323
00:15:51,684 --> 00:15:54,284
WHO COULD EVER LOVE
THAT SELFISH, ARROGANT MONSTER?

324
00:15:54,317 --> 00:15:56,784
- WHO'S SHE TALKING ABOUT?
- I DON'T KNOW.

325
00:15:56,817 --> 00:15:58,717
- HMPH!

326
00:16:01,151 --> 00:16:03,917
YOU'RE ON.
I'LL GO TO THE MOVIES WITH YOU.

327
00:16:03,951 --> 00:16:06,984
- THAT'S GREAT!
ALL RIGHT!

328
00:16:07,017 --> 00:16:08,184
[SIGH]

329
00:16:08,217 --> 00:16:11,384
- WHO DOES INUYASHA THINK HE IS,
TRYING TO CONTROL MY LIFE?

330
00:16:11,417 --> 00:16:15,384
I'LL TAKE THINGS
INTO MY OWN HANDS.
THAT'LL SHOW HIM.

331
00:16:20,517 --> 00:16:23,184
UHH.
[GRUNTS]

332
00:16:23,917 --> 00:16:25,517
I PULLED A MUSCLE THAT TIME.

333
00:16:25,551 --> 00:16:30,017
I HOPE INUYASHA'S
GETTING A GOOD REST.

334
00:16:30,051 --> 00:16:31,317
- OPEN UP!

335
00:16:31,351 --> 00:16:32,884
LET ME OUT OF HERE!

336
00:16:32,917 --> 00:16:35,351
- YOU'RE WASTING YOUR TIME,
INUYASHA.

337
00:16:35,384 --> 00:16:37,017
THIS HUT IS COVERED
WITH SACRED SEALS

338
00:16:37,051 --> 00:16:39,117
TO KEEP THE DEMONS OUT
AND YOU IN.

339
00:16:39,151 --> 00:16:42,317
- YEAH, BUT WHO SAYS
I NEED TO BE SEALED INSIDE?

340
00:16:42,351 --> 00:16:45,451
OPEN UP!
- PLEASE STOP, INUYASHA.

341
00:16:45,484 --> 00:16:46,517
BE STILL AND REST.

342
00:16:46,551 --> 00:16:50,484
YOUR INJURIES STILL HAVEN'T
HAD ENOUGH TIME TO HEAL.

343
00:16:50,517 --> 00:16:52,951
- KAGOME.

344
00:16:52,984 --> 00:16:54,051
[GIGGLING]

345
00:16:54,084 --> 00:16:56,284
- I COULD LIE WITH YOU
IF YOU LIKE.

346
00:16:56,317 --> 00:16:58,717
- SHIPPO, YOU CREEP!

347
00:16:58,751 --> 00:17:00,917
LAUGH IT UP, FUZZBALL!

348
00:17:00,951 --> 00:17:03,017
- I WAS ONLY TRYING
TO CHEER YOU UP!

349
00:17:03,051 --> 00:17:04,351
UNH! UNH! OOH! OOH! OW!

350
00:17:04,384 --> 00:17:07,184
- YOU'VE BEEN KNOCKING AROUND
INSIDE THIS PLACE
FOR HOURS ALREADY.

351
00:17:07,217 --> 00:17:10,951
- YEAH!
SO HURRY UP AND UNTIE ME!
- THEN THE DEMONS WOULD GET YOU.

352
00:17:10,984 --> 00:17:12,884
THUS THE SEALED HUT
WOULD BE MEANINGLESS.

353
00:17:12,917 --> 00:17:14,851
- UNH!
LET ME OUT OF HERE!

354
00:17:14,884 --> 00:17:16,217
UNH!
AH!

355
00:17:16,251 --> 00:17:19,417
- KAEDE, SEAL THE DOOR
WITH THE SACRED ENCHANTMENT.

356
00:17:19,451 --> 00:17:20,384
- CONSIDER IT DONE.

357
00:17:20,417 --> 00:17:23,084
- YOU MUSTN'T RUSH THINGS,
INUYASHA.

358
00:17:23,117 --> 00:17:25,484
I AM INCLINED TO WANT
TO RUSH AFTER NARAKU, AS WELL,

359
00:17:25,517 --> 00:17:28,184
BUT FIRST YOU MUST
RECOVER FROM YOUR INJURIES.

360
00:17:28,217 --> 00:17:29,217
- HE SPEAKS THE TRUTH.

361
00:17:29,251 --> 00:17:31,317
NARAKU'S STRENGTH IS ALWAYS
BEYOND COMPREHENSION.

362
00:17:31,351 --> 00:17:36,951
ISN'T THAT PRECISELY WHY
YE BANISHED KAGOME
TO HER OWN WORLD?

363
00:17:36,984 --> 00:17:37,717
- IT IS?

364
00:17:37,751 --> 00:17:39,784
HE SENT HER AWAY OUT OF CONCERN?

365
00:17:39,817 --> 00:17:41,184
- WE NEED YOU
TO RECOVER QUICKLY,

366
00:17:41,217 --> 00:17:43,317
FOR WE MUST FACE NARAKU
AT OUR STRONGEST.

367
00:17:43,351 --> 00:17:46,451
OTHERWISE, I FEAR THAT
OUR FATES WILL BE SHORT-LIVED.

368
00:17:46,484 --> 00:17:48,184
- UHH.
ARE YOU A MAN OR A MOUSE?

369
00:17:48,217 --> 00:17:51,084
I, FOR ONE, AM PREPARED
TO FIGHT NARAKU HERE AND NOW!

370
00:17:51,117 --> 00:17:56,017
- PUT YOUR HEAD DOWN
AND GET YOURSELF SOME
MUCH-NEEDED SLEEP, MY GOOD MAN.

371
00:17:56,051 --> 00:17:57,784
LIE DOWN!
BE SILENT!

372
00:17:57,817 --> 00:17:58,584
SLEEP!
REST!

373
00:17:58,617 --> 00:18:00,051
HOW MANY TIMES
DO I HAVE TO TELL YOU?

374
00:18:00,084 --> 00:18:03,317
- MIROKU, AIM FOR
THE OLD INJURIES.

375
00:18:04,284 --> 00:18:06,717
- INUYASHA, YOU AWAKE?

376
00:18:06,751 --> 00:18:07,951
- UH...WHY?

377
00:18:07,984 --> 00:18:12,384
- I WAS THINKING ABOUT KAGOME
AND WONDERING IF SHE MISSES US.

378
00:18:12,417 --> 00:18:13,817
- YOU WOKE ME UP FOR THAT?

379
00:18:13,851 --> 00:18:15,017
FORGET ABOUT KAGOME.

380
00:18:15,051 --> 00:18:16,251
SHE'S A THING OF THE PAST.

381
00:18:16,284 --> 00:18:18,617
I MEAN, THE FUTURE.
- HMM?

382
00:18:18,651 --> 00:18:20,784
- AS LONG AS SHE'S
ALIVE AND WELL,

383
00:18:20,817 --> 00:18:22,584
THAT'S ALL I HOPE FOR.

384
00:18:22,617 --> 00:18:26,484
I CAN'T BEAR TO SEE
ANOTHER WOMAN DIE.

385
00:18:26,517 --> 00:18:29,084
[WHIMPERING]

386
00:18:31,717 --> 00:18:35,517
- I'VE BEEN
SEARCHING FOR YOU, ROYAKAN.

387
00:18:35,551 --> 00:18:37,584
- NARAKU?

388
00:18:38,551 --> 00:18:39,784
GO AWAY!

389
00:18:39,817 --> 00:18:44,517
I REFUSE TO BATTLE
WITH INUYASHA AGAIN.
- WHY DO YOU TREMBLE SO?

390
00:18:44,551 --> 00:18:48,451
- I HAVE NO DESIRE TO BE
DRAWN INTO A WIND TUNNEL.

391
00:18:48,484 --> 00:18:49,551
[CHUCKLING]

392
00:18:49,584 --> 00:18:55,184
- I SHALL TAKE AWAY YOUR FEAR
AND STOP YOUR TREMBLING.

393
00:18:55,217 --> 00:18:57,551
- [INDISTINCT]

394
00:18:59,151 --> 00:19:01,717
[SCREAMING]

395
00:19:13,551 --> 00:19:15,717
AAAH!

396
00:19:15,751 --> 00:19:18,284
[ROARING]

397
00:19:20,884 --> 00:19:23,017
[CHUCKLING]

398
00:19:23,051 --> 00:19:26,917
- A SINISTER WIND BLOWS OUR WAY.

399
00:19:28,117 --> 00:19:30,017
LADY KAEDE, STAY ON GUARD,

400
00:19:30,051 --> 00:19:32,817
FOR A MALEVOLENT SPIRIT
APPROACHES.

401
00:19:32,851 --> 00:19:34,251
- AYE.

402
00:19:34,284 --> 00:19:36,951
[DOG BARKING]

403
00:19:36,984 --> 00:19:39,884
WE SHALL STOP HIM HERE.
- HMM.

404
00:19:43,217 --> 00:19:48,517
- INUYASHA, WHERE ARE
YOU HIDING?

405
00:19:48,551 --> 00:19:49,851
- HE'S COME BACK!

406
00:19:49,884 --> 00:19:53,051
AND HE'S EVEN LARGER THAN
LAST TIME!

407
00:19:53,084 --> 00:19:55,884
- REVEAL YOURSELF, INUYASHA.

408
00:19:55,917 --> 00:19:58,217
- AS LONG AS OUR SPELL
IS UNBROKEN,

409
00:19:58,251 --> 00:20:02,084
INUYASHA'S HUT SHALL REMAIN
INVISIBLE TO THE DEMON.

410
00:20:02,117 --> 00:20:03,851
- WHAT HAS CAUSED
THIS TRANSFORMATION?

411
00:20:03,884 --> 00:20:06,484
THE BEAST IS EVEN MORE
FRIGHTFUL THAN BEFORE.

412
00:20:06,517 --> 00:20:09,817
I'LL WAGER THAT ANOTHER SHARD
OF THE SACRED SHIKON JEWEL

413
00:20:09,851 --> 00:20:11,984
HAS BEEN EMBEDDED IN HIS BODY.

414
00:20:12,017 --> 00:20:15,351
- WHAT A PITIFUL DEFENSE.

415
00:20:15,384 --> 00:20:16,817
HUH!

416
00:20:18,317 --> 00:20:19,251
- NO!

417
00:20:19,284 --> 00:20:20,151
- DON'T MOVE.

418
00:20:20,184 --> 00:20:22,284
- I HAVE NO CHOICE!

419
00:20:29,184 --> 00:20:31,251
- THERE YOU ARE!

420
00:20:31,284 --> 00:20:33,784
[ROARS]

421
00:20:35,351 --> 00:20:41,751
- INUYASHA!

422
00:20:41,784 --> 00:20:44,517
- UHH.
- I OWE YOU ONE, ROYAKAN,

423
00:20:44,551 --> 00:20:45,784
FOR GETTING ME OUT OF THAT HUT,

424
00:20:45,817 --> 00:20:49,451
WHERE MY SO-CALLED FRIENDS,
THE MONK AND THAT HAG,

425
00:20:49,484 --> 00:20:50,784
SEALED ME INSIDE.

426
00:20:50,817 --> 00:20:53,084
- FOR YOUR PROTECTION,
I MIGHT ADD.

427
00:20:53,117 --> 00:20:55,551
- GRATITUDE DOESN'T
COME NATURALLY TO HIM.

428
00:20:55,584 --> 00:20:58,451
- I HAVE HEARD ENOUGH!

429
00:20:58,484 --> 00:21:00,817
- LET'S GET AT IT!

430
00:21:04,117 --> 00:21:05,817
[GRUNTING]

431
00:21:05,851 --> 00:21:09,217
AAH!
UNH!

432
00:21:09,251 --> 00:21:10,284
UHH.

433
00:21:10,317 --> 00:21:12,751
- INUYASHA'S BEEN THROWN
TO THE GROUND.

434
00:21:12,784 --> 00:21:13,784
- HE MAY HAVE THE WILL TO FIGHT,

435
00:21:13,817 --> 00:21:16,284
BUT HIS STRENGTH HASN'T
HAD TIME TO RECOVER YET.

436
00:21:16,317 --> 00:21:21,084
- I'M NO MATCH FOR HIS MIGHT.
HUH?

437
00:21:22,417 --> 00:21:25,017
- [INDISTINCT]
THE SACRED JEWEL.

438
00:21:25,051 --> 00:21:28,184
- I HAVE TO GET IT
BEFORE HE DOES.

439
00:21:29,284 --> 00:21:31,551
- HANDS OFF, DEMON!

440
00:21:31,584 --> 00:21:32,551
- SHIPPO!

441
00:21:32,584 --> 00:21:34,051
- YOU WON'T ESCAPE.

442
00:21:34,084 --> 00:21:35,384
[ROARS]

443
00:21:35,417 --> 00:21:37,884
- AAH!
AH! AH!

444
00:21:37,917 --> 00:21:42,184
- SHIPPO, MOVE!
I'LL OPEN MY WIND TUNNEL!

445
00:21:42,217 --> 00:21:43,851
[GASP]
- LOOK!

446
00:21:43,884 --> 00:21:46,717
- NARAKU'S VENOMOUS INSECTS.

447
00:21:49,751 --> 00:21:51,351
[GRUMBLES]

448
00:21:51,384 --> 00:21:52,384
- IT FIGURES.

449
00:21:52,417 --> 00:21:55,284
NOW, HOW DO WE GET OURSELVES
OUT OF THIS ONE?

450
00:21:55,317 --> 00:21:57,884
[SCREAMING]

451
00:22:08,806 --> 00:22:12,540
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

452
00:23:37,440 --> 00:23:38,606
- 50 YEARS EARLIER,

453
00:23:38,640 --> 00:23:41,573
INUYASHA AND KIKYO
WERE DECEIVED INTO THINKING

454
00:23:41,606 --> 00:23:42,740
THEY HAD BETRAYED ONE ANOTHER,

455
00:23:42,773 --> 00:23:46,006
AND IT WAS THE DEMON NARAKU
WHO HAD STAGED THE TREACHERY.

456
00:23:46,040 --> 00:23:48,573
WHY HAD HE DONE SUCH A THING?
WHAT WAS HIS PURPOSE?

457
00:23:48,606 --> 00:23:52,040
INUYASHA'S WRATH AND HIS
BURNING MEMORIES OF KIKYO

458
00:23:52,073 --> 00:23:54,673
FINALLY LEAD HIM
TO NARAKU'S HIDDEN LOCATION.

459
